N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 97.2 - Computation of fees

State Regulations

The fee for any such beer license shall be equal to the
respective annual fee specified in the Alcoholic Beverage Control Law
multiplied by the number of years for which such license is
issued. Notes
